data.message: BrandForge MVP Phase 5 self-review and bug fixes: Fixed 6 critical issues: (1) Added template pack selector UI - was completely missing, (2) Added ProcessingStatus component with 3-second polling for auto-refresh, (3) Added error/success feedback to brand-kit-editor, (4) Added error handling and display to batch-actions and proof-grid, (5) Removed unused projectId prop from ProofGrid, (6) Added loading states for regenerate button. All phases 0-5 now complete with self-review.
